# Devopness MCP server

## Run

### Shell

```shell
uv run main.py
```

### Shell - with MCP inspector

```shell
# Using Anthropic's official MCP inspector
uv run mcp dev main.py

# Using alpic.ai MCP inspector
npx @alpic-ai/grizzly uv run main.py
```

