### Cursor
**~/.cursor/mcp.json**:
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "Devopness": {
      "command": "uv",
      "args": [
        "--directory",
        "/full/path/to/devopness/packages/ai/mcp-server/",
        "run",
        "main.py"
      ],
      "env": {
        "DEVOPNESS_USER_EMAIL": "<email address>",
        "DEVOPNESS_USER_PASSWORD": "<password>",
      }
    }
  }
}

```


